OL,3,CMan still suffering flashbacks after
OL,4,Cbeing 'spiked by a friend'
OL,6,FDrink spiking is not a new phenomenon
OL,7,F- in Bristol or any other city - but
OL,8,Fas a society, we still haven't cracked
OL,9,Fhow to stamp it out for good.
OL,11,FOne woman who has felt the effects of
OL,12,Fthis is Simone White, from Bradley
OL,13,FStoke, who ended up unable to walk or
OL,14,Fspeak while out for brunch with a
OL,15,Ffriend.
OL,17,FFive weeks on, she still can't drive
OL,18,Fdue to the lasting effects of a drug
OL,19,Fshe believes was used to spike her
OL,20,Fdrink.
