OL,4,Cbeing 'spiked by a friend'
OL,6,FAged 43, Simone believed she was safe
OL,7,Ffrom a crime that predominantly
OL,8,Faffects women between the ages of 18
OL,9,Fand 35, according to data from Avon
OL,10,Fand Somerset Police.
OL,12,FDrink spiking can leave an indelible
OL,13,Fmark on all its victims - as Harry
OL,14,F(not his real name) can confirm.
OL,16,FHe was walking home from a house party
OL,17,Fduring his time at university when the
OL,18,Fnight took a sinister turn.
OL,20,FEven five years on, he becomes
OL,21,Femotional when speaking about it.
