OL,3,CMan still suffering flashbacks after
OL,4,Cbeing 'spiked by a friend'
OL,6,FHarry said: "A tiny part of me still
OL,7,Fdoesn't know what happened. One night
OL,8,FI went to a friend's house party and I
OL,9,Fwas trying to keep it chilled and not
OL,10,Fhave a crazy blackout night.
OL,12,F"I had some wine with me, but it was
OL,13,Fway too rich so I didn't finish it. I
OL,14,Fwas taking it very easy, I was very
OL,15,Flucid.
OL,17,F"I decided to leave the party and
OL,18,Fthere was a guy there who was a friend
OL,19,Fof a friend. Looking back on it, there
OL,20,Fwas always something a bit off about
OL,21,Fhim.
