OL,3,CMan still suffering flashbacks after
OL,4,Cbeing 'spiked by a friend'
OL,6,F"We were friendly, but not close
OL,7,Ffriends, and we were walking home that
OL,8,Fnight.
OL,10,F"We were standing at this lookout
OL,11,Fspot, looking over the city, sharing a
OL,12,Fbeer and having a cigarette there."
OL,14,FThat's the last full memory Harry has
OL,15,Fof the night. Everything after that
OL,16,Fpoint is "blurry", he explained.
OL,18,F"I remember stumbling around and
OL,19,Ftrying to walk home and this guy,
OL,20,Fwell, he didn't seem to want to help
OL,21,Fme get home.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUtD@cO]xD@JOUxD@QO]zD@AOU
