OL,3,CMan still suffering flashbacks after
OL,4,Cbeing 'spiked by a friend'
OL,6,F"I remember falling a little bit and
OL,7,Fthen suddenly being very angry about
OL,8,Fhim behind me.
OL,10,F"Then I remember getting up and
OL,11,Fpulling my trousers up and that's all
OL,12,Fthe series of events that I can link
OL,13,Ftogether.
OL,15,F"I don't know to what degree anything
OL,16,Fhappened but I woke up the next day
OL,17,Ffeeling a bit sore. I had cuts all
OL,18,Fdown my legs and I had no idea how I
OL,19,Fblacked out."
