OL,3,CMan still suffering flashbacks after
OL,4,Cbeing 'spiked by a friend'
OL,6,F"It was only when I saw him again, and
OL,7,Fhe gave me a look of pure disgust,
OL,8,Fthat it affirmed for me that something
OL,9,Fhad gone on, because he was never like
OL,10,Fthat before with me," he said.
OL,12,FIt wasn't until 2021 - over a year
OL,13,Fafter the night Harry believes he was
OL,14,Fspiked - that he opened up about what
OL,15,Fhappened.
OL,17,F"My friend said she wasn't going out
OL,18,Fbecause there was a protest against
OL,19,Fdrink spiking that meant all the girls
OL,20,Fwere staying in.
