OL,3,CMan still suffering flashbacks after
OL,4,Cbeing 'spiked by a friend'
OL,6,F"I just didn't want it to have
OL,7,Fhappened at the start. I just wanted
OL,8,Fto carry on as normal because as soon
OL,9,Fas you accept something like that you
OL,10,Fhave to deal with it," he said.
OL,12,FLater, after Harry discussed the
OL,13,Fincident with another of his friends,
OL,14,Fhe found out a bit more about the man
OL,15,Fhe believes spiked him.
OL,17,F"They were like 'oh I'm really sad to
OL,18,Fhear this', but they weren't
OL,19,Fsurprised. They believed that he was
OL,20,Fcapable of that.
