OL,3,CMan still suffering flashbacks after
OL,4,Cbeing 'spiked by a friend'
OL,6,F"Finding out a bit about him
OL,7,Fafterwards, I think he'd been around a
OL,8,Flot of rough situations himself and I
OL,9,Fthink he had experience with drugs
OL,10,Flike GHB.
OL,12,F"That's when the realisation sunk in
OL,13,Fthat something really had happened. It
OL,14,Falso made me wonder if I could trust
OL,15,Fmyself because I wondered if I'd got
OL,16,Finvolved in it."
OL,18,FHarry added that, even now, he
OL,19,Fstruggles to let his guard down around
OL,20,Fother men.
