OL,3,CMan still suffering flashbacks after
OL,4,Cbeing 'spiked by a friend'
OL,6,F"I felt a lot of male guilt around it,
OL,7,Fbecause I had trauma that was caused
OL,8,Fby a man, but I was still attracted to
OL,9,Fmen, and I was a man myself. You
OL,10,Fproject a lot of what someone has done
OL,11,Fto you onto yourself.
OL,13,F"I remember going along to a vigil for
OL,14,FSarah Everard and there was just this
OL,15,Fcircle of women shouting 'f*** men,
OL,16,Ff*** men'.
OL,18,F"Being on the outside, I just wanted
OL,19,Fto talk about how I was feeling, but I
OL,20,Ffelt like I couldn't."
