OL,6,FHarry has been in therapy for a few
OL,7,Fyears and said he had a "breakthrough"
OL,8,Flast autumn that helped him feel
OL,9,Fcomfortable dating again.
OL,11,FIf you have been affected by any of
OL,12,Fthe issues raised in this report,
OL,13,Fthere is help available to you. Visit
OL,14,Fthe charity for support, resources and
OL,15,Fguidance. If you believe you have been
OL,16,Fa victim of crime, contact your local
OL,17,Fpolice force to report it.
