OL,3,CMan still suffering flashbacks after
OL,4,Cbeing 'spiked by a friend'
OL,6,FHe said: "It's still fresh for me,
OL,7,Fthis recovery and this change. I can
OL,8,Fdefinitely get triggered a bit still.
OL,9,FI felt a wall go up and it took me a
OL,10,Fwhile to take it down.
OL,12,F"It still has an effect on me, I'm not
OL,13,Fable to explore that side of my
OL,14,Fsexuality as much as I'd like.
OL,16,F"I will always warn people if I hear
OL,17,Fof someone being predatory but I have
OL,18,Fto be careful not to project my own
OL,19,Ftrauma onto other people."
