OL,6,FIn 2022-23, Avon and Somerset Police
OL,7,Freceived 600 reports of spiking.
OL,8,FAround 75% of victims were female and
OL,9,Fpeople aged 18-39 were mostly likely
OL,10,Fto be targeted.
OL,12,FAround 82% of victims don't know who
OL,13,Fhas spiked them, and around 21% of
OL,14,Fvictims are from the LGBT community.
OL,16,FThe force says it will always take
OL,17,Freports of drink spiking seriously.
OL,19,F"We know it can be scary to report,
OL,20,Fbut we are here to help you", a
OL,21,Fspokesperson said.
